OL,7,FMinisters proposed to spend #9.5
OL,8,Fmillion on a multi-option referendum,
OL,9,Fwhich would see Scots asked if they
OL,10,Fbacked increased powers for Holyrood `
OL,11,Fand then if these powers should be
OL,12,Fextended to "allow independence to be
OL,13,Fachieved".
OL,15,FAt the time the plans were announced,
OL,16,Fin February 2010, Mr Salmond insisted
OL,17,Fthey would give Scots a "vital say on
OL,18,Fthe country's future".
