OL,7,FMinisters went on to launch a
OL,8,Fconsultation on their Referendum Bill
OL,9,Fplans, but opposition from other
OL,10,Fparties at Holyrood meant the
OL,11,Flegislation was never formally
OL,12,Fintroduced.
OL,14,FIn May 2011, the SNP won an
OL,15,Funprecedented majority in the Scottish
OL,16,FParliament ` with this success leading
OL,17,Fdirectly to the independence
OL,18,Freferendum of 2014.
