OL,5,Creveal
OL,7,FHowever, newly released cabinet papers
OL,8,Ffrom 2010 reveal ministers had
OL,9,Fconsidered holding their multi-option
OL,10,Freferendum on the same say as the 2011
OL,11,FScottish election.
OL,13,FPapers, released from 15 years ago,
OL,14,Findicate the vote could be held in
OL,15,FMarch 2011 or "on the same day as the
OL,16,FScottish Parliament election on May 5
OL,17,F2011".
