OL,7,FThe document also reveals there had
OL,8,Fbeen "no engagement with the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment on our proposals" from the
OL,10,FScottish government.
OL,12,FBut Scottish government officials at
OL,13,Fthe time had had "regular discussions"
OL,14,Fwith the Electoral Commission "about
OL,15,Fthe detail of holding a referendum",
OL,16,Fthe paper said.
