OL,3,CMinisters considered holding indyref
OL,4,Con same day as 2011 election, papers
OL,5,Creveal
OL,7,FHolding a referendum on the same day
OL,8,Fas the 2011 Scottish Parliament vote
OL,9,F"could lead to potentially significant
OL,10,Fcost savings as the apparatus for
OL,11,Fholding a national poll has to be in
OL,12,Fplace for that day anyway", it noted.
OL,14,FConcerns, however, were raised that
OL,15,Fthose responsible for running the 2011
OL,16,Felection would be "taken by surprise"
OL,17,Fif a referendum was proposed for the
OL,18,Fsame date and "their likely initial
OL,19,Freaction would be extremely negative,
OL,20,Fprobably to the extent of publicly
OL,21,Fcriticising this approach".
