OL,5,Creveal
OL,7,FThe document stated the proposed
OL,8,Fballot would "in effect, be a
OL,9,Fconsultation with the people of
OL,10,FScotland".
OL,12,FBut it added: "The Scottish
OL,13,Fgovernment's expectation is that the
OL,14,FUK government and Parliament would
OL,15,Flisten to the views of the people and
OL,16,Fact on them as they have done in all
OL,17,Fother referendums held in the UK."
