OL,7,FAlthough the Scottish government did
OL,8,Fnot proceed with holding a multi-
OL,9,Foption referendum, the Holyrood
OL,10,Felection in 2011 took place on the
OL,11,Fsame day as the UK Conservative and
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat coalition government
OL,13,Fheld a referendum on a possible switch
OL,14,Fto proportional representation for
OL,15,FWestminster elections.
OL,17,FVoters rejected the option of moving
OL,18,Fto the alternative vote system.
